<plot>This "Bow and Arrow Adventures" entry was filmed on an unidentified island off the coast of Southern California, where wild boars run freely. 'Howard Hill (I)' (qv), billed as the "world's greatest archer," shows his speed and accuracy shooting at stationary targets, birds in flight, and a charging wild boar.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?656649</url></doc>
